  "text": "The aim of this paper is to remedy this frustration by solving [CITATION_1] and three other equations of the same type. Each of them defines the generating function of a class of pattern-avoiding permutations that can be described by a bi-labelled generating tree: we thus recover and refine, in a unified way, some results on Baxter permutations, 1234-avoiding permutations and 54321-avoiding involutions.",
